titles.title: Electing Members to certain standing committees of the House of Representatives and ranking Members on a certain standing committee of the House of Representatives.
Electing Members to certain standing committees of the House of Representatives and ranking Members on a certain standing committee of the House of Representatives.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary:
This resolution elects specified Members to the House Committees on (1) the Budget, (2) Ethics, (3) Natural Resources, and (4) Rules.
In addition, the resolution ranks a specified Member on the House Committee on Rules.
